      <section eId="sec_419_040">
        <num>419.040</num>
        <content>
          <p>The judge granting the writ
    may require bond conditioned that the person detained shall not escape by
    the way, and for the payment of costs. The bond shall be filed with the record
    of the proceedings, and shall be sued on by the Commonwealth for the benefit
    of anyone injured by the breach of it.</p>
